text.tspan: Your page on Export Portal will have a special link by
your choice which will help your company to be
instantly recognized by your customers.
Export Portal ID will present your company in the best
light. As well as the detailed information on larger
number of pages which you can use on your company
webpage.
You will be able to verify products and confirm status
of products. Plus your products can be promoted on our
front page by allowing inquiry, making offer or PO
requests.
For your offline customers you can have a certificate
to expose in your office which will show your global
coverage.
You will receive a free membership with EXIMA, Export
Portals partner organization.
Your products will be shared on our networks partner
sites which allows to sell more and gain constant flow
of deals.
You will be assisted with company posts, uploading
photos and videos, updating news and events.
You will get a possibility to connect your Export
Portal page to all your social media pages: Facebook,
LinkedIn, Instagram, Skype, Twitter
